FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777043470
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FThe youth centres will help young
OL,7,Fpeople aged up to 18 with employment
OL,8,Fadvice, health and wellbeing, and are
OL,9,Falso aimed at preventing them from
OL,10,Ffalling into a life of crime.
OL,12,FAreas of high anti-social behaviour
OL,13,Fhave been targeted for the first wave
OL,14,Fof the hubs, but they will be among 50
OL,15,Fwhich will open across the country.
OL,17,FBristol's new East Central Bristol
OL,18,FYoung Futures Hub, based at Full
OL,19,FCircle Docklands in St Paul's, was
OL,20,Famong the first to open its doors on 1
OL,21,FApril.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777043470
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FIt is the only Young Futures Hub in
OL,7,Fthe South West of England, and one of
OL,8,Fjust eight local authorities selected
OL,9,Fas an early adopter of the programme.
OL,11,FBristol will receive almost #1 million
OL,12,Fto help develop the model locally.
OL,14,FCulture Secretary Lisa Nandy said:
OL,15,F"The closure of over a thousand youth
OL,16,Fcentres since 2010 didn't just take
OL,17,Faway facilities, it took away
OL,18,Fcommunity, connection and opportunity
OL,19,Ffor a generation. We are determined to
OL,20,Frebuild that.
OL,26,@wD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777043470
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,F"These hubs are about more than bricks
OL,7,Fand mortar, they're a statement that
OL,8,Fthis Government believes in young
OL,9,Fpeople and is investing in their
OL,10,Ffutures.
OL,12,F"What makes them different is that
OL,13,Fwe're joining things up ` wellbeing
OL,14,Fsupport, crime prevention, work
OL,15,Fcoaches, youth services, all in one
OL,16,Fplace.
OL,18,F"We're making sure teenagers have
OL,19,Fsomewhere to go, someone to talk to
OL,20,Fand a real chance to thrive."
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOUzD@AOU|D@]O]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
