OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777043470
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FIn Bristol, the Hub operates on a "hub
OL,7,Fand spoke" model, with Full Circle
OL,8,FDocklands at its centre, working
OL,9,Falongside a partnership of local
OL,10,Fvoluntary organisations including Off
OL,11,Fthe Record, Empire Fighting Chance,
OL,12,FCreative Youth Network and Bristol
OL,13,FCity Council's post-16 team.
OL,15,FCouncillor Christine Townsend, Chair
OL,16,Fof the Children and Young People
OL,17,FCommittee, said the Hub reflects
OL,18,FBristol's ambition to build
OL,19,F"neighbourhood-based, preventative
OL,20,Fservices" that support young people
OL,21,Fwithin their own communities.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777043470
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FYoung people at the Bristol launch
OL,7,Fwere enthusiastic. Kodi Kondwani, 18,
OL,8,Fsaid: "I think that the new youth hub
OL,9,Fwill be the start of something big,
OL,10,Fthe opening just shows me that there
OL,11,Fis hope for the youth."
OL,13,FThe offer at each hub is expected to
OL,14,Fgrow as learning from the early stages
OL,15,Fshapes future activity, with the
OL,16,FNational Youth Agency describing
OL,17,FBristol's approach as having "a clear
OL,18,Fand ambitious" commitment to involving
OL,19,Fyoung people in shaping local services.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777043470
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FYoung people aged between 10 and 18,
OL,7,Fas well as those with special
OL,8,Feducational needs and disabilities
OL,9,F(Send) up to the age of 25, will be
OL,10,Fable to access services at the youth
OL,11,Fcentres.
OL,13,FThe drive to open new youth hubs comes
OL,14,Famid a Government crackdown on knife
OL,15,Fcrime due to launch this week.
OL,17,FMinisters are hoping to halve knife
OL,18,Fcrime over the course of a decade as
OL,19,Fpart of a plan called Protecting
OL,20,FLives, Building Hope.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
