OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,436,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1777043470
OL,3,CBristol to benefit from new youth
OL,4,Cclubs to curb anti-social behaviour
OL,6,FSarah Jones, the policing minister,
OL,7,Fsaid: "Knife crime devastates lives.
OL,9,F"Behind every statistic is a child who
OL,10,Fdidn't make it home, a family whose
OL,11,Fworld has been shattered, and a
OL,12,Fcommunity left with fear.
OL,14,F"This Government will halve knife
OL,15,Fcrime within a decade, saving lives
OL,16,Fand protecting communities.
OL,18,F"We will roll out young futures hubs
OL,19,Fin crime hotspots across the country
OL,20,Fto divert young people from violence,
OL,21,Fcut crime and protect communities."
OL,26,@oD@GOUqD@AOUzD@AOU}D@cO]
